Dialogue: 0,0:00:04.09,0:00:09.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,宇迦之御魂（倉稻魂尊）病毒是那麼容易就能調整的嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:00:09.49,0:00:13.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因為作業工程基本是全自動的
Dialogue: 0,0:00:13.64,0:00:15.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只要設備依舊能運作
Dialogue: 0,0:00:15.61,0:00:19.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,說到底 宇迦之御魂的優勢就在於易於更新
Dialogue: 0,0:00:20.43,0:00:24.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒想到良性病毒會變成貨真價實的病原體
Dialogue: 0,0:00:24.74,0:00:27.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,本以為是能保障糧食自給的鐵之壁壘
Dialogue: 0,0:00:27.75,0:00:29.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,實際上是把雙刃劍啊
Dialogue: 0,0:00:31.23,0:00:32.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,起飛吧
Dialogue: 0,0:01:10.67,0:01:13.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,耶穌做出了另一個比喻
Dialogue: 0,0:01:15.38,0:01:18.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,把天國做了如下比喻
Dialogue: 0,0:01:18.93,0:01:21.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,某個人把良種植入稻田
Dialogue: 0,0:01:22.35,0:01:24.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在人們還在夢鄉之時敵人來襲
Dialogue: 0,0:01:25.61,0:01:29.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在小麥中摻入了有毒的小麥
Comment: 0,0:00:01.00,0:00:01.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~OP~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~
Dialogue: 0,0:01:33.87,0:01:36.39,opc,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I would like to show
Dialogue: 0,0:01:36.39,0:01:40.39,opc,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Cut open my skull look into my head
Dialogue: 0,0:01:40.78,0:01:43.27,opc,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I don't know why I'm so harsh
Dialogue: 0,0:01:43.27,0:01:44.96,opc,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I can't be so brash
Dialogue: 0,0:01:45.00,0:01:46.92,opc,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I'm going to crash
Dialogue: 0,0:01:46.92,0:01:50.17,opc,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,'Cause I feel
Dialogue: 0,0:01:50.41,0:01:56.95,opc,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I can't always show my everything to you
Dialogue: 0,0:01:57.27,0:02:01.03,opc,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,If this moment was for me
Dialogue: 0,0:02:01.12,0:02:04.54,opc,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I try to hear,lend my ear
Dialogue: 0,0:02:04.54,0:02:10.53,opc,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Voices inside one link to join it all
Dialogue: 0,0:02:10.76,0:02:11.96,opc,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Again
Dialogue: 0,0:02:24.68,0:02:27.92,opc,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,'Cause I feel
Dialogue: 0,0:02:28.08,0:02:34.65,opc,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I can't always show my everything to you
Dialogue: 0,0:02:34.96,0:02:38.71,opc,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,If this moment was for me
Dialogue: 0,0:02:38.79,0:02:42.16,opc,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I try to hear,lend my ear
Dialogue: 0,0:02:42.16,0:02:48.21,opc,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Voices inside one link to join it all
Dialogue: 0,0:02:48.42,0:02:51.44,opc,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,So it goes
Dialogue: 0,0:02:51.95,0:02:53.07,opc,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Again
